#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:294
#, python-format
msgid "This is %(username)s's read-only shared map."
msgstr "これは%(username)sさんの閲覧専用の共有地図です。"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:296
msgid "Click a prefecture on the map to update its status."
msgstr "地図上の都道府県をクリックしてステータスを更新できます。"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:300
#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:348
msgid "lived in"
msgstr "在住"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:301
#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:352
msgid "stayed overnight"
msgstr "宿泊"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:302
#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:356
msgid "walked in"
msgstr "散歩"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:303
#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:360
msgid "passed through"
msgstr "通過"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:345 templates/update.html:126
msgid "What do the categories mean?"
msgstr "カテゴリーの意味"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:349 templates/update.html:134
msgid ""
"Places you called home for a while, even if it was only one chapter of life."
msgstr ""
"しばらく暮らして、自分の生活の拠点だった場所。人生の一章だけでもここに入りま"
"す。"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:353 templates/update.html:138
msgid ""
"Places where you slept at least one night, from hotels to friends' couches."
msgstr "ホテルでも友だちの家でも、少なくとも一泊した場所。"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:357 templates/update.html:142
msgid ""
"Places where your feet actually touched the ground and you spent a little "
"time there."
msgstr "実際にその土地を歩いて、少しでも時間を過ごした場所。"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:361 templates/update.html:146
msgid ""
"Places you traveled through without really stopping, like a train transfer "
"or road trip crossing."
msgstr "電車の乗り換えや車での通過など、しっかり滞在せずに通り過ぎた場所。"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:366
msgid "Share your map"
msgstr "地図を共有"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:369
msgid "Open shared map"
msgstr "共有地図を開く"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:376
msgid "Details:"
msgstr "詳細："

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:394
msgid ""
"Turn your travels into a bright little map: mark the places you have lived, "
"where you stayed overnight, where you wandered on foot, and the places you "
"only breezed through on the way to somewhere else."
msgstr ""
"旅の思い出を、カラフルな小さな地図にしましょう。住んだ場所、泊まった場所、歩"
"いてめぐった場所、そして目的地へ向かう途中で通り過ぎた場所まで記録できます。"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:395
msgid ""
"It is part diary, part scoreboard, and part gentle nudge to make your next "
"ordinary trip feel like it belongs in the story too."
msgstr ""
"日記のようで、スコアボードのようで、次の何気ないお出かけも物語の一部にしたく"
"なる、そんな旅の記録帳です。"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:397
msgid "Start your map"
msgstr "地図をはじめる"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:398
msgid "Log in to your map"
msgstr "自分の地図にログイン"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:422
msgid "Account Email"
msgstr "メール管理"

#: templates/travelregistration/homepage.html:424
msgid "Account Password"
msgstr "パスワード管理"

#: templates/update.html:89
msgid "Update Location"
msgstr "地域更新"

#: templates/update.html:96 templates/update.html:98
#, python-format
msgid "Click a button to update the status for %(prefecture)s prefecture."
msgstr ""
"%(prefecture)sのステータスを更新するには、ボタンをクリックしてください。"

